These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, thriller, family
1. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | classical     | house    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Movie-Genre         | epic | family | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, wooden
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, teacher
1. the teacher is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the wooden house is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the musician is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the teacher is in an even position##4
6. the teacher is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| House   | wooden | farmhouse | cape-cod    |
| Job     | dancer      | teacher    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, plum
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bluemaster, dunhill
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating apple##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | apple         | plum     | kiwi   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster       | bongani     | dunhill |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, teacher, writer
3 different games are played: whist, chess, monopoly
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the writer##1
3. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the teacher is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | writer | teacher  | social-worker |
| Game        | whist | chess | monopoly         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, satire, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
There 3 different types of food: spinach, onion, papaya
1. the american is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
2. the australian is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance  | satire  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Food           | onion  | papaya    | spinach    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, carrot, grapefruit
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the person eating corn is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Food    | grapefruit  | corn  | carrot        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
3 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, rat
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, baking, skydiving
1. the person watching sports movies is between the owner of the frog and the person watching western movies##2
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports        | western |
| Pet           | frog   | goldfish      | rat     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | baking | video-games    |

