.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, collecting, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, june, may
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, rat
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | collecting | camping | rock-climbing |
| Birthday   | may       | june  | february     |
| Pet           | rabbit     | rat     | goat          |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, rugby, soccer
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, thai
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the german is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the chef is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the thai is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| Sport   | rugby | soccer | handball    |
| Nationality   | thai         | german      | russian |

