.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, cooking, hiking
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, mechanic, musician
City: marseilles, venice, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the musician##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping     | hiking   |
| Job           | mechanic  | electrician | musician |
| City   | san-francisco | venice     | marseilles |

