.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-18::.
House: cottage, art-deco, tower
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, train
1. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the tower house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| House    | cottage | tower      | art-deco     |
| Pet         | lizard  | goldfish | rat        |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train    | helicopter |

